summary: A very well-equipped, yet simple player home. Kinda cheater-ish, because you don\'t have to do anything to deserve it.
descriptionHtml:
A very well-equipped, yet simple player home. Kinda cheater-ish, because you don\'t have to do anything to deserve it. Includes the following amenities:
Bookshelves
Bed
Merchant (fence)
Mannequins (more than 30)
Enchanting and alchemy tables
Smelter, forge, workbench, grinder
Ample storage. 

Fully navmeshed, but thanks to a CK bug, your companions still won\'t follow you. Great. 

The entrance is right next to the forge in Whiterun. Just look around next to the smelter. 


Version .9:
Uploaded to Skyrim Nexus. 
All 31 mannequins downstairs work. 
Bookshelves are a little wonky, because they are scripted for a specific mod. 
Weapon racks off of the main chamber don\'t really work, thanks to another CK bug. The weapons just kind of float off to the side.
author: Sleepyjoe256
